AdGuard Home is a network-wide software for blocking ads and tracking.
After you set it up, it will cover ALL your home devices, and you do not
need any client-side software for that.

It operates as a DNS server that re-routes tracking domains to a "black
hole", thus preventing your devices from connecting to those servers. It
is based on software used for public AdGuard DNS servers, and both are
free of charge.

WWW: https://adguard.com/en/adguard-home/overview.html
